For Most New Yorkers who love the Healthy lifestyle, this probably is night the place for you.  But if your in the mood for a fun date or a night out with your friends, Korzo is a great place to come.    The alcoholic drinks are great and the ribs are unreal.  They have a deal for unlimited bloody Marys.  If you like them go for it; too many Bloody Marys can get pretty intense
